Name: Caporn St & Franklin Rd, Mariginiup
Description: Travelling North on Franklin Rd most traffic turns left into Caporn St. The traffic facing Franklin Rd from Caporn St has a Give Way sign and many cars assume they do not need to stop there as the vehicles on Franklin will turn into Caporn.  Some do not. Numerous accidents have happened at this intersection and some of these could be prevented either by way of a Stop sign or, more appropriately given the high volume, a round about.  Also, many poorly patched potholes at that end of Caporn St.
